'''Ankou''' are skeletal, ghostly monsters. Ankou in the fourth level of the [[Stronghold of Security]] can drop the [[left skull half]], one of four parts of the [[Skull sceptre]].

Ankou are popular monsters for their common [[death rune|death]] and [[blood rune]] drops. They can be assigned as slayer tasks by [[Vannaka]], [[Nieve]]/[[Steve]], [[Krystilia]], [[Duradel]] and [[Konar quo Maten]].

