==Tips==
The [[Salve amulet]] works on this monster as it is an [[undead]] creature. However, if Ankous are your Slayer task, the [[Salve amulet]] does '''not''' stack with the bonus received by the [[Slayer helmet|Slayer Helmet]], and the former's bonus will take priority.

There is a safespot at [[The Forgotten Cemetery]], located behind the south-west coffin, on the square between the bone spawns. Beware of [[Player killing|player killers]] as this is around level 30 [[Wilderness]]. 

Furthermore there is a safespot located in the [[Stronghold of Security]]: [[Sepulchre of Death]] floor. This spot can be found in the south-west room, by standing on the south side of the south-easternmost skeleton. 

To speed up an ankou slayer task, a [[dwarf multicannon]] can be used in the [[Wilderness Slayer Cave]], as well as in the [[Stronghold Slayer Cave]].

